&lt;h2 id="part-1">Part 1&lt;/h2>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Given a &lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/directed%20graph">directed graph&lt;/a> defined where &lt;code>aaa: you hhh&lt;/code> means &lt;code>aaa&lt;/code> is connected to &lt;code>you&lt;/code> and &lt;code>hhh&lt;/code>, how many paths are there from &lt;code>you&lt;/code> to &lt;code>out&lt;/code>.&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote></description></item><item><title>AoC 2025 Day 7: Laser Splittinator</title><link>https://blog.jverkamp.com/2025/12/07/aoc-2025-day-7-laser-splittinator/</link><pubDate>Sun, 07 Dec 2025 00:00:03 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.jverkamp.com/2025/12/07/aoc-2025-day-7-laser-splittinator/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="source-day-7-laboratories">Source: &lt;a href="https://adventofcode.com/2025/day/7" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Day 7: Laboratories&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
